Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  貓  貓  貓…
