Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,332)\fs16\fsp2}TreeDiagram
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有辦法拯救她們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪將要參加接下來的實驗  御阪說道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  求你了
